## Tailwind Usage

- Use Tailwind v4 utility classes for styling; avoid inline `style` unless necessary.
- Compose classes with the `cn` helper from [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts). Example: `className={cn("p-4", isActive && "bg-foreground")}`.
- Prefer semantic spacing and sizing tokens where available; avoid magic numbers.
- Keep class lists readable: group by layout, box-model, typography, color, state.
